---
import Layout from '@layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '@components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '@components/Footer.astro';

const lang = 'en' as const;
---

<Layout lang={lang}>
  <Header lang={lang} />
  <main class="py-24 lg:py-32">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-text-muted mb-8">Last updated: March 8, 2026</p>

      <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none space-y-6 text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-text mt-8 mb-4">1. Data Controller</h2>
        <p>ANGA Mexico (&quot;Anga Security&quot;), based in Mexico City, Mexico, is the data controller for your personal data. Contact email: <a href="mailto:jose301184@gmail.com" class="text-primary hover:underline">jose301184@gmail.com</a>.</p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-text mt-8 mb-4">2. Data We Collect</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li><strong>Account data:</strong> email address, password (hashed), name (if provided).</li>
          <li><strong>Technical data:</strong> analyzed domain name, Cloudflare Zone ID, API tokens (encrypted in transit, never stored).</li>
          <li><strong>Usage data:</strong> generated reports, credits consumed, transaction history.</li>
          <li><strong>Payment data:</strong> processed directly by MercadoPago. We do not store card numbers.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-text mt-8 mb-4">3. Purpose of Processing</h2>
        <p>We use your data to:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li>Provide security audit, simulation, and compliance services.</li>
          <li>Generate and store security reports associated with your account.</li>
          <li>Process payments and manage credits.</li>
          <li>Send service-related communications.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-text mt-8 mb-4">4. Storage and Security</h2>
        <p>Your data is stored in Supabase (cloud infrastructure) with encryption at rest and in transit. Cloudflare API tokens are transmitted securely and are <strong>not stored</strong> after analysis execution.</p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-text mt-8 mb-4">5. Data Sharing</h2>
        <p>We do not sell or share your personal data with third parties, except:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li><strong>MercadoPago:</strong> for payment processing.</li>
          <li><strong>Cloudflare API:</strong> to execute security analyses (using your own tokens).</li>
          <li><strong>Supabase:</strong> as our database and authentication provider.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-text mt-8 mb-4">6. Your Rights</h2>
        <p>Under applicable data protection laws (including Mexico&apos;s LFPDPPP and, where applicable, GDPR), you have the right to access, rectify, delete, or object to the processing of your personal data. To exercise these rights, email <a href="mailto:jose301184@gmail.com" class="text-primary hover:underline">jose301184@gmail.com</a>.</p>

        <h2 id="cookies" class="text-xl font-bold text-text mt-8 mb-4">7. Cookies</h2>
        <p>We use essential cookies for authentication and session management. We do not use advertising tracking cookies.</p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-text mt-8 mb-4">8. Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>We reserve the right to update this privacy policy. Any changes will be published on this page.</p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-text mt-8 mb-4">9. Contact</h2>
        <p>For any privacy inquiries: <a href="mailto:jose301184@gmail.com" class="text-primary hover:underline">jose301184@gmail.com</a></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
  <Footer lang={lang} />
</Layout>
